elements.text:
Using Excalidraw to manage todos and ideas

- Learn Astro
    - Island arch
- Learn Partytown 
    - Manage 3rd scripts
- Learn WSAM
    - With Rust?
- Learn Web Worker
- Learn Service Worker
- Learn Animation
- Learn WebGL
- Latest Frontend Tech
    - Codux - Vistual component editor
- Software Engineering
     - Don't try to break the UI application into multiple repo just because we have multiple squad.
if you don't have module federation, it just introduce lots of limitation to the application.
    - Company should leverage the tech to increase produbility
    - Don't spend time on meetings that doesn't have agenda and no clear goal
    - Enterprise means lots of department, lots of controls, lots of governance, meaning moving slow?
    - If you thank someone, they might thank you back.
    - Pushing teams with a deadline will just produce crapy code. 
- Use ChatGPT to generate content.
- Learn AI?
